<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation says that toFloat truncates the return value, but it doesn't. It returns the rounded value. Probably that's just a documentation problem?</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 
require_once 'Zend/Locale.php';

$locale = new Zend_Locale('de_DE');
$number =1.5555;

$opts = array ('locale'=&gt;$locale, 'precision'=&gt;0);
echo Zend_Locale_Format::toFloat($number, $opts);
// puts out  2


$opts = array ('locale'=&gt;$locale, 'precision'=&gt;2);
echo Zend_Locale_Format::toFloat($number, $opts);
// 1,56
</code></pre>

